@node Whatcrt "WHAT ARE .crt rom cartridge images?"

WHAT ARE .crt rom cartridge IMAGES?
-----------------------------------
.crt files are well..dumps of C-64 cartridge ROMs with a header attached, and are 
used in the CCS64 C-64 emulator.

A normal C-64 (or current Amiga C-64 emulators) cannot properly load these files, 
so...I added support for them to und64, and it happily converts them into
c-64 style files (and directly loadable on a c-64 or emulator).

@endnode

